t: "Do not approach an orphanÂṀs estate before he comes of age, except to improve it. Grant full measure and weight in all fairness. We do not assign person to do more than he can cope with. Whenever you speak, be just even though it concerns a close relative. Fulfill GodÂṀs agreement. Thus has He instructed you so that you may bear it in mind"